{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"tag"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"V"},{"kind":"text","text":">("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"tag"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"V"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"includeOptional"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"},{"kind":"text","text":" = true) -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","text":"View"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"where"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"V"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SH","text":"Hashable"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/swift\/hashable"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value to use as the view’s tag."}]}],"name":"tag"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the tag value for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Optional<V>"},{"type":"text","text":" should"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"also be set."}]}],"name":"includeOptional"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view with the specified tag set."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier to differentiate among certain selectable views,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"like the possible values of a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"type":"text","text":" or the tabs of a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"TabView"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Tag values can be of any type that conforms to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/swift\/hashable","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This modifier will write the tag value for the type "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"V"},{"type":"text","text":", as well as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Optional<V>"},{"type":"text","text":" if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"includeOptional"},{"type":"text","text":" is enabled. Containers checking for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tags of either type will see the value as set."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In the example below, the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ForEach"},{"type":"text","text":" loop in the "},{"code":"Picker","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"builder iterates over the "},{"code":"Flavor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" enumeration. It extracts the string"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value of each enumeration element for use in constructing the row"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"label, and uses the enumeration value as input to the "},{"code":"tag(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"modifier."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct FlavorPicker: View {","    enum Flavor: String, CaseIterable, Identifiable {","        case chocolate, vanilla, strawberry","        var id: Self { self }","    }","","    @State private var selectedFlavor: Flavor? = nil","","    var body: some View {","        Picker(\"Flavor\", selection: $selectedFlavor) {","            ForEach(Flavor.allCases) { flavor in","                Text(flavor.rawValue)","                    .tag(flavor)","            }","        }","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The selection type of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"type":"text","text":" is an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Optional<Flavor>"},{"type":"text","text":" and so it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"will look for tags on its contents of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Optional<Flavor>"},{"type":"text","text":"type. Since the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tag modifier defaults to having "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"includeOptional"},{"type":"text","text":" enabled, even though"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the tag for each option is a non-optional "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Flavor"},{"type":"text","text":", the tag modifier"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"writes values for both the non-optional, and optional versions of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value, allowing the contents to be selectable by the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ForEach","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" automatically applies a default tag to each enumerated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"id"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter of the corresponding element. If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the element’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"id"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter and the picker’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"selection"},{"type":"text","text":" input"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"have exactly the same type, or the same type but optional, you can omit"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the explicit tag modifier."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To see examples that don’t require an explicit tag, see ","type":"text"},{"code":"Picker","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack\/tag(_:includeOptional:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"platforms":[{"beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","name":"iOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false},{"beta":false,"introducedAt":"10.15","name":"macOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false},{"beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","name":"tvOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false},{"beta":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","name":"visionOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false},{"beta":false,"introducedAt":"6.0","name":"watchOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false}],"title":"tag(_:includeOptional:)","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewPAAE3tag_15includeOptionalQrqd___SbtSHRd__lF::SYNTHESIZED::s:15OpenSwiftUICore6VStackV","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tag","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"V","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"includeOptional","kind":"externalPara